I had been all in on wireless charging for years.  Even before apple incorporated into the phones themselves i had Qi charging cases for my iPhone 5,6 and 7.  

However, with the advent of fast charging with usb-c i don’t use wireless much anymore. 30 minutes on fast charging twice a day and I’m good.
Prob fake.  Stupid Tik Tok type stuff everything is fake and staged now its gotten pathetic.
